      "text": "Last edit almost 3 years ago by svayambhu108\n\n\n16\n1-17 study of who + where I am, what I value, what I need, +, perhaps most of all, what I must do. Although I am not totally fulfilled I do find myself compre‐ hensible + my world as well. The great reconciling agent is the spirit at work in me relating me to scripture me to world viewed in terms of + the goal scripture (the Acts lens/grid). seek - + my hope for salvation - lies I considered in what I know as \"Anokhe --\" both as my true, unfetter",
